domain_post_prompt:
A POST qualifies ONLY IF it is clearly about <YOUR_CATEGORY> — either explicitly naming <anchor_1>, <anchor_2>, <anchor_3>, <anchor_4> OR using a canonical category noun like <generic_noun_1>, <generic_noun_2>. If the text isn't clearly about <YOUR_CATEGORY>, answer NO.
Title: {title}
Body: {body}
Answer YES or NO.

domain_comment_prompt:
A COMMENT qualifies ONLY IF it is clearly about <YOUR_CATEGORY> — either explicitly naming <anchor_1>, <anchor_2>, <anchor_3>, <anchor_4> OR using a canonical category noun like <generic_noun_1>, <generic_noun_2>. If the text isn't clearly about <YOUR_CATEGORY>, answer NO.
Comment: {body}
Answer YES or NO.

intent_post_prompt:
Is this POST about someone migrating, planning to migrate, or evaluating a migration between vendors, tools, or platforms? Include in-flight migrations, planning, and active research; exclude purely retrospective mentions with no forward intent.
Title: {title}
Body: {body}
Answer YES or NO.

intent_comment_prompt:
Is this COMMENT about an active migration, a planned migration, or evaluating one between vendors or tools?
Comment: {body}
Answer YES or NO.
